15 SECTION 2.
16 Said Act is further amended by revising subsection (a) of Section 3 as follows:
17 "SECTION 3
18 Randolph County Airport Authority.
19 (a) There is created a body corporate and politic, to be known as the 'Randolph County
20 Airport Authority,' which shall be deemed to be a political subdivision of the State of
21 Georgia and a public corporation and by that name, style, and title said body may contract
22 and be contracted with, sue and be sued, implead and be impleaded, and bring and defend
23 actions in all courts. The authority shall have perpetual existence."
24 SECTION 3.
25 Said Act is further amended by revising paragraph (2) of subsection (a) of Section 4 as
26 follows:
27 "(2) 'Authority' means the Randolph County Airport Authority created by this Act."
28 SECTION 4.
29 Said Act is further amended by revising Section 6 as follows:
30 "SECTION 6.
31 Successor to former airport authority.
32 The Randolph County Airport Authority shall be the successor in interest to the Lower
33 Chattahoochee Regional Airport Authority created by an Act approved May 5, 2006
34 (Ga. L. 2006, p. 4422), as amended, and shall by operation of law acquire and assume all
